lines.text: Mike you asshole, don't go solo, you know procedure! Second time!
What's your problem man? The hard work's over.
We're supposed to be partners! And you think you're Dirty Goddamn Harry and you are not making my goddamn day!
Hey man, I don't work good with partners.
You don't work good with anybody. You pull this Lone Ranger shit again and you can say goodbye to Tonto.
